<paragraph blockId="12.[130,775,663,1135]" box="[132,222,663,689]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">REMARK</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[130,775,663,1135]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">
Reviewing different plants collected from 
<collectingRegion box="[567,771,694,720]" country="Iran" name="Kordestan" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Kurdistan province</collectingRegion>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[130,243,726,752]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="insignis">
<emphasis box="[130,243,726,752]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">C. insignis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is reported as a new record from 
<collectingCountry box="[615,661,726,752]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Iran</collectingCountry>
(
<figureCitation box="[677,763,726,752]" captionStart="FIG" captionStartId="12.[813,824,867,884]" captionTargetBox="[906,1362,215,823]" captionTargetId="figure-694@12.[906,1362,215,824]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIG. 8. — Cotoneaster insignis Pojark. leaves and fruits outline (A) and close up (B). Collection number:Attar, Raei Niaki &amp; Zamani 37454 (TUH);determined by Raei Niaki &amp; Attar." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6573129" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6573129/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Fig. 8A</figureCitation>
). The species belongs to subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority="(Fryer &amp; Hylmo 2009)" baseAuthorityName="Fryer &amp; Hylmo" baseAuthorityYear="2009" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Chaenopetalum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[501,669,758,784]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Chaenopetalum</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="FRYER J. &amp; HYLMO B." pageId="12" pageNumber="151" refId="ref4629" refString="FRYER J. &amp; HYLMO B. 2009. - Cotoneasters: A Comprehensive Guide to Shrubs for Flowers, Fruit, and Foliage. Timber press, Portland, London, 344 p." type="book" year="2009">Fryer &amp; Hylmö 2009</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. As noted above, 
<taxonomicName box="[481,593,790,816]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="insignis">
<emphasis box="[481,593,790,816]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">C. insignis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[648,775,790,816]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ellipticus">
<emphasis box="[648,775,790,816]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">C. ellipticus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are closest relatives. Other than morphological differences, these species are geographically distinct. So, 
<taxonomicName box="[594,700,854,880]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="insignis">
<emphasis box="[594,700,854,880]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">C. insignis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurs in west of 
<collectingCountry box="[243,291,886,912]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Iran</collectingCountry>
, while 
<taxonomicName box="[365,490,885,912]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ellipticus">
<emphasis box="[365,490,885,912]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">C. ellipticus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurs in the northeast of 
<collectingCountry box="[131,180,918,944]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Iran</collectingCountry>
. Consequently, the morphological differences and the discontinuous distribution provide sufficient evidence for treating 
<taxonomicName box="[225,350,981,1007]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ellipticus">
<emphasis box="[225,350,981,1007]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">C. ellipticus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[403,515,981,1007]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="insignis">
<emphasis box="[403,515,981,1007]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">C. insignis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as separate species. The geographical distribution of the 
<taxonomicName box="[490,603,1013,1039]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="insignis">
<emphasis box="[490,603,1013,1039]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">C. insignis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is 
<collectingCountry box="[634,771,1013,1039]" name="Afghanistan" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Afghanistan</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[132,262,1045,1071]" name="Kyrgyzstan" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Kyrgyzstan</collectingCountry>
, Azerbaijan, 
<collectingCountry box="[414,530,1045,1071]" name="Tajikistan" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Tajikistan</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[545,608,1045,1071]" name="India" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">India</collectingCountry>
, northwestern Himalaya (
<bibRefCitation author="RIEDL H." box="[259,385,1077,1103]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" pagination="13 - 26" refId="ref5495" refString="RIEDL H. 1969. - Cotoneaster Medik., in RECHINGER K. H. (ed.), Flora Iranica. Akademische Druck und Verlagsanstalt, Graz 66: 13 - 26." type="journal article" year="1969">Riedl 1969</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="POJARKOVA A. I." box="[403,578,1077,1103]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" pagination="259 - 274" refId="ref5207" refString="POJARKOVA A. I. 1971. - Cotoneaster Medik., in KOMAROV V. L. (ed.), Flora of USSR. Keter press, Jerusalem 9: 259 - 274." type="journal article" year="1971">Pojarkova 1971</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="FRYER J. &amp; HYLMO B." pageId="12" pageNumber="151" refId="ref4629" refString="FRYER J. &amp; HYLMO B. 2009. - Cotoneasters: A Comprehensive Guide to Shrubs for Flowers, Fruit, and Foliage. Timber press, Portland, London, 344 p." type="book" year="2009">Fryer &amp; Hylmö 2009</bibRefCitation>
) and west of 
<collectingCountry box="[342,391,1109,1135]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Iran</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6573129" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6573129" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6573129/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" startId="12.[813,824,867,884]" targetBox="[906,1362,215,823]" targetPageId="12">
<paragraph blockId="12.[813,1455,867,929]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">
FIG. 8. — 
<taxonomicName authority="Pojark." authorityName="Pojark." box="[895,1133,867,884]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="insignis">
<emphasis box="[895,1066,867,884]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Cotoneaster insignis</emphasis>
Pojark.
</taxonomicName>
leaves and fruits outline (
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1349,1362,867,884]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">A</emphasis>
) and close up (
<emphasis bold="true" box="[843,856,889,906]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">B</emphasis>
). Collection number: 
<emphasis box="[1031,1300,889,906]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Attar, Raei Niaki &amp; Zamani 37454</emphasis>
(TUH);determined by Raei Niaki &amp; Attar.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="12.[131,776,1173,1358]" box="[133,199,1173,1199]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">NOTE</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[131,776,1173,1358]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">
This species has been reported from 
<collectingCountry box="[533,579,1205,1231]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Iran</collectingCountry>
without mention of the locality (
<bibRefCitation author="RIEDL H." box="[295,417,1236,1262]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" pagination="13 - 26" refId="ref5495" refString="RIEDL H. 1969. - Cotoneaster Medik., in RECHINGER K. H. (ed.), Flora Iranica. Akademische Druck und Verlagsanstalt, Graz 66: 13 - 26." type="journal article" year="1969">Riedl 1969</bibRefCitation>
). So, this species was not verified as a native species for 
<collectingCountry box="[387,433,1269,1295]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Iran</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="KHATAMSAZ M." box="[453,643,1268,1294]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" pagination="209 - 239" refId="ref4690" refString="KHATAMSAZ M. 1992. - Cotoneaster Medik., in ASSADI M. (ed.), Flora of Iran. Research institute of forests and rangelands publication, Tehran 6: 209 - 239 [in Persian]." type="journal article" year="1992">Khatamsaz 1992</bibRefCitation>
). However, this species was found from west 
<collectingCountry box="[502,548,1301,1327]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Iran</collectingCountry>
and is introduced as a new record based on the collected data.
</paragraph>
